title: Niwa ni wa Niwa Niwatori ga ita
description:
A strange world where aliens have taken over the human world, and only two humans are left which are apparently disguising themselves as mere chickens.

Fujimoto Tatsuki's first one-shot when he was only 17, and it also contains a special interview section!
